{"tid":1911090,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(武漢肺炎) 川普：對疫情不感意外，幾月前就曾隱密地從中国聽聞","createTime":"2020-03-05T06:20:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-05T08:51:21.000Z","uid":184679,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d5bcf128b056dd900967e5fec538b459d4ea3c7a","tid":1911090,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T06:20:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.moneydj.com/z/sjn/jpg/GetNewsRptjpg.djjpg?a=202792\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.moneydj.com%2Fz%2Fsjn%2Fjpg%2FGetNewsRptjpg.djjpg%3Fa%3D202792&h=84d6391d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n新型冠狀病毒肺炎(正式名稱為COVID-19、又稱武漢肺炎)全球爆發、讓許多國家措手不及，但美國總統川普(Donald Trump)在最新專訪中直指，他對疫情其實不感意外。<br />\n<br />\nFox Business報導，川普在美東時間4日晚間受訪時表示，他在幾個月前，就曾「非常隱密地」(very quietly)從中國聽聞武漢肺炎疫情。<br />\n<br />\n川普並說，隔離從中國返鄉的公民，是他「非常明智的決定」，這減緩病毒在美國擴散的速度。即便有許多顧問都說，將每位去過中國的旅客進行篩檢、為時太早，但他仍堅持這麼做。「這也是我國現在需要擔憂的確診人數這麼低的主因。」<br />\n<br />\n目前全美有129個確診病例、11人不幸死亡。全球的確診病例則超過93,000起、約3,100人死亡。<br />\n<br />\n根據白宮發布的新聞稿，川普2日在接受記者採訪時指出，他已要求製藥廠加速研發疫苗的速度。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.moneydj.com/KMDJ/News/NewsViewer.aspx?a=324759ed-5858-4de6-92c0-59311c9b4162\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.moneydj.com%2FKMDJ%2FNews%2FNewsViewer.aspx%3Fa%3D324759ed-5858-4de6-92c0-59311c9b4162&d=%2BwrRK7ySmiC6A5TqlPyaq3yU4AarvyINc8S1qmu5ZLM%3D&h=334a2ef4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.moneydj.com/KMDJ/News/NewsViewer.aspx?a=324759ed-5858-4de6-92c0-59311c9b4162</a>"},{"pid":"68cf6348b6eab445c57cc93adf6aa3a93f2adc75","tid":1911090,"uid":33653,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T06:21:40.000Z","msg":"出黎啦，五毛。"},{"pid":"d4b1047e359449a6bf20f24ac4e56aa58512d86b","tid":1911090,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T06:23:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2575000/2576037/P7_600.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2575000%2F2576037%2FP7_600.png&h=1a59ce25&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"17625b66bbd4589f1e40b466c342f40c7d7f89eb","tid":1911090,"uid":226466,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d4b1047e359449a6bf20f24ac4e56aa58512d86b","tid":1911090,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T06:23:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2575000/2576037/P7_600.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2575000%2F2576037%2FP7_600.png&h=1a59ce25&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T06:30:10.000Z","msg":"所有野 從古至今都係 屬於中國<br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎病毒 🦠 都唔例外<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e09e43293c4b6949ab7d539ccd21490a544c69d","tid":1911090,"uid":33263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T08:40:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/S9Zzg9C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FS9Zzg9C.jpg&h=5242a9cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n厲害了，我的國"},{"pid":"0f703641d943c1e2f9221797683b59e86ece6f53","tid":1911090,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T08:51:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}